73
00:02:40,495 --> 00:02:42,163
Ok, tudo bem.

74
00:02:42,247 --> 00:02:43,873
CLARE:
Obrigada!

75
00:02:43,957 --> 00:02:45,458
(SINAL TOCA)

76
00:02:48,253 --> 00:02:49,712
Uau! Ah!

77
00:02:49,796 --> 00:02:51,381
Presidente Torres,
trabalhando duro.

78
00:02:51,464 --> 00:02:52,799
Devo trazer minha prancha de surfe
amanhã?

79
00:02:52,882 --> 00:02:53,550
